{"article_id":"em3dDqcdfHEK9Epn","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"In ABC TV interview , former FBI director says","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"US president treats women like meat","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"and was a ' stain ' on everyone","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"who worked for him","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"James Comey has accused Donald Trump of being \" morally unfit \"","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"to be president","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"and treating women like \" meat \" in his first television interview in support of his new book , A Higher Loyalty .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Comey further described Trump as a \" stain \" on everyone","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"who worked for him ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"according to a transcript of a five-hour interview","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"published by ABC","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"and first obtained by the New York Times .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"Yet Comey said","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"he does not wish for Trump ' s impeachment","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"because that \" would let the American people off the hook \" .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"ABC News","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"( @ ABC ) .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"@ GStephanopoulos :","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"\" Is Donald Trump unfit to be president ? \"","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"@ Comey :","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"\" Yes ,","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"but not in the way","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"I often hear people talk about it ...","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"I do n't think","depth":13},{"id":24,"text":"he 's medically unfit to be president .","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"I think","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"he 's morally unfit","depth":14},{"id":27,"text":"to be president. \"","depth":14},{"id":28,"text":"https : //t.co/nzGYlTmLXf # Comey pic.","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"twitter.com/4eag9flFZ","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"2","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"\" People in this country need to stand up","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"and go to the voting booth","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"and vote their values , \"","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"Comey said .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"\" And impeachment in a way would short-circuit that . \"","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"A one-hour edited version of the interview with George Stephanopolous aired on ABC News on Sunday night .","depth":4},{"id":37,"text":"Five things","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"we learned from the James Comey interview","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"Read more","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"\" Our president must embody respect","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"and adhere to the values","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"that are at the core of this country , \"","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"Comey told Stephanopoulos .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"\" The most important being truth .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"This president is not able to do that .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"He is morally unfit to be president . \"","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"Turning first to Trump ' s defence of a white supremacists ' march ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"he said :","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"\" A person","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"who sees moral equivalence in Charlottesville ,","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"who talks about and treats women","depth":15},{"id":52,"text":"like they ' re pieces of meat ,","depth":15},{"id":53,"text":"who lies constantly about matters big and small","depth":15},{"id":54,"text":"and insists","depth":16},{"id":55,"text":"the American people believe it ,","depth":16},{"id":56,"text":"that person ' s not fit to be president of the United States , on moral grounds . \"","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"Replying to a question","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"about whether Trump had committed an obstruction of justice ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"Comey said","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"\" it ' s possible \" .","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"\" There ' s certainly some evidence of obstruction of justice , \"","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"Comey said .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"But for the president to follow through on threats","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"to fire special counsel Robert Mueller ,","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"Comey said ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"would \" set off alarm bells","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"that this is his most serious attack yet on the rule of law \" .","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"In his book , Comey compares Trump to a mafia don","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"and challenges the president ' s character , honesty and commitment to public service .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"Sitting in his Virginia living room across from Stephanopolous ,","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"Comey answered questions about the Trump team ' s response to Russian election tampering , about his handling of the Clinton emails investigation and his personal impressions of the president-elect .","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"\" He had impressively coiffed hair","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"that looks to be all his , \"","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"Comey said .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"\" I confess","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"I stared at it pretty closely ...","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"He looked slightly orange up close with small white half-moons under his eyes","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"which I assume","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"were from tanning goggles . \"","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Comey also described the \" really weird \" Trump Tower meeting","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"in which he briefed the president-elect on the contents of an unverified intelligence document","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"compiled by former British spy Christopher Steele ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"including allegations","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"that Trump had been in a Moscow hotel room in 2013 with urinating Russian prostitutes .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"\" I did not go into the business","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"about people peeing on each other \" in his briefing with Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"Comey said .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"\" I just wanted to get it done","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"and get out of there . \"","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"It was \" unlikely \" but \" possible \" that Russians had material","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"with which to blackmail or otherwise compromise Trump ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Comey said .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"\" It is stunning ,","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"and I wish","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"I wasn ' t saying it ,","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"but it ' s the truth . \"","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"I did not go into the business","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"about people peeing on each other ..","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"I just wanted to get it done","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"and get out of there","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"James Comey","depth":4},{"id":102,"text":"Comey spoke for the first time about his immediate family ' s disappointment at Hillary Clinton ' s loss .","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"his four daughters and his wife , Patrice Comey , all wanted Clinton to win ,","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"and","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"as the ABC broadcast showed pictures of them protesting ,","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"Comey disclosed","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"they attended the Women ' s March in Washington a day after Trump ' s inauguration .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"Comey responded to criticism by Clinton and others","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"that he had cost her the election","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"by making public a late-stage twist in an investigation of her emails .","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"After the election ,","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"Comey said ,","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"he felt \" vaguely sick to my stomach ,","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"feeling beaten down .","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"I felt","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"that I was totally alone ,","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"that everybody hated me ,","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"and that there was no way out","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"because it was the right thing","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"to do \" .","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"But Comey said","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"he would make the same decision again ,","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"quoting verbatim from his book :","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"\" Down that path lies the death of the FBI as an independent force in American life . \"","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"Comey described his intense discomfort at his first meeting with the president , at a reception for law enforcement officials at the White House two days after the election .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"Comey tried to camouflage himself in the drapery","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"but was spotted by Trump","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"and called across the room ,","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"video of which moment has been widely circulated .","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"Play Video 3:23 Trump and Comey ' s hate-hate relationship - video explainer","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"Patrice Comey called the look on his face in the video \" Jim ' s Oh Shit face , \"","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"Comey said .","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"Comey also detailed a one-on-one dinner with Trump in the Green room of the White House","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"at which he said","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"Trump asked for his pledge of loyalty","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"- an account","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"Trump has denied .","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"Trump made his pitch \" after the salad but before the shrimp scampi \" ,","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"Comey said .","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"The former FBI director said","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"- not wanting to give the president any signals","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"and realizing the gravity of the moment -","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"that he thought to himself :","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"\" Don ' t you dare move . \"","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"Comey dismissed Trump ' s denial of a different scene ,","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"in which Comey said","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"Trump told him to \" let go \" of an investigation of former national security adviser Michael Flynn .","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"\" The president says","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"he didn ' t say that , \"","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"Stephanopoulos said .","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"\" What am I gon na do ?","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"He did , \"","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"Comey replied with a shrug .","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"Brisk pre-sales for the book , and the ambitious national tour","depth":5},{"id":156,"text":"Comey has planned","depth":6},{"id":157,"text":"beginning in New York City on Tuesday ,","depth":6},{"id":158,"text":"have prompted criticism about the amount of money","depth":6},{"id":159,"text":"Comey seems to be making","depth":6},{"id":160,"text":"as he settles scores with the president .","depth":5},{"id":161,"text":"Yet Comey ' s career as a government prosecutor speaks to the seriousness of his commitment to the public good ,","depth":4},{"id":162,"text":"and whatever other motivations he may have","depth":6},{"id":163,"text":"for going in front of the cameras ,","depth":6},{"id":164,"text":"Comey clearly sees Trump as a threat to the country","depth":6},{"id":165,"text":"and sees himself as capable","depth":7},{"id":166,"text":"of defending it .","depth":7},{"id":167,"text":"James Comey helped Trump win .","depth":5},{"id":168,"text":"Now he wants to undo his mistake |","depth":5},{"id":169,"text":"Richard Wolffe","depth":4},{"id":170,"text":"Read more","depth":5},{"id":171,"text":"Comey described his reaction","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"to finding out on TV , during a trip to California ,","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"that he had been fired less than halfway through his 10-year term .","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"\" That ' s crazy , \"","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"Comey remembered thinking .","depth":9},{"id":176,"text":"\" How could that be ? \"","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"Then Comey got on the FBI plane for the long flight back to Washington .","depth":7},{"id":178,"text":"\" I drank red wine from a paper coffee cup","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"and just looked out at the lights of the country","depth":10},{"id":180,"text":"I love so much","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"as we flew home . \"","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"The White House did not reply to a query","depth":6},{"id":183,"text":"about whether Trump planned to watch the Comey interview ,","depth":7},{"id":184,"text":"which was taped earlier in the week .","depth":7},{"id":185,"text":"Trump did not tweet during the broadcast .","depth":6},{"id":186,"text":"However , Ronna McDaniel , Republican National Committee chairwoman , said on Twitter","depth":7},{"id":187,"text":"that Comey had \" no credibility \"","depth":8},{"id":188,"text":"and \" his true higher loyalty is to himself \" .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":377,"left":343,"right":376,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":343,"left":225,"right":342,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":225,"left":192,"right":224,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":192,"left":0,"right":191,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":191,"left":1,"right":190,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":190,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":224,"left":223,"right":36,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":223,"left":202,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":199,"right":201,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":199,"left":194,"right":198,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":194,"left":193,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":1